      • placeItem

        public void placeItem(Item item,
                      GeoCasheHistorys casheHistorys)
        This method places an item in a geocache. It uses geocacheID to find the correct cache and then associates the item with the cache by setting the geocashe's item id to the item's id passed as a parameter. This method then adds the geocache id and email to geocacheHistorys.
